{
  "stem": "393.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't know why they needed so much-- by the hundreds.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We made-- we made 200 radios every day-- 200-- maybe more-- thousands.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That was a-- a-- assembly work, which I never saw, you know, with the band-- move in the middle.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We pushed.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They teached us.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They taught us how to do it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we learned very fast-- very, very fast.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The lager was very small-- of course, fenced.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But-- but we had, each of us, a bed-- a bed, yeah-- with a blanket.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And we had a bowl.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we had a piece of soap.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We never had that-- and a-- a towel, also, a small bathroom.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We had that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We had one dress, just what we had on us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sometimes, I think, oh, how was it?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But-- but someday, when we didn't work, we washed it, and we dried it somehow.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] That was one hour going to the factory-- the factory was called Florence.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember the factory's name-- and one hour coming back.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We worked 12 hours a day.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had a 1/2 an hour lunch time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Then, they gave us later, only the later months, some kind of a soup.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We got the food when we came home from the factory, as it was day and night shift.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I worked a couple of months daytime and then a couple of months nighttime.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Somehow, I liked better the nighttime.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The night went faster than the day.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We were always hungry-- always hungry-- constantly.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And when we had a little leisure time, we talked about food-- how you cook this, how you cook this, oh, my mother made that or what.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Guben wasn't so terrible but we were, of course, prisoners.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
